  <brief_title>Study of Peri-Operative Docetaxel Plus Laparoscopic Radical Prostatectomy in Prostate Cancer Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective Phase II of Peri-Operative Docetaxel + Laparoscopic Radical Prostatectomy in Patients With Localized Gleason 7 pT2a-pT2b Adenocarcinoma and a Risk of Relapse After Radical Prostatectomy</official_title>
