  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a prospective phase II study of peri-operative docetaxel plus laparoscopic radical
      prostatectomy in patients with localized Gleason 7 pT2a-pT2b adenocarcinoma of the prostate
      and a risk of relapse after radical prostatectomy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
